Dialogue: 0,0:01:20.25,0:01:22.96,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}在時間線上遍地盛開的FAKE
Dialogue: 0,0:01:23.29,0:01:24.33,OPCN,,0,0,0,,{\fad(200,200)\be5}What is reality?
